name: Mojito
description:
Mojito by @Sykcoloart

https://linktr.ee/sykcolo

4000  ×  4000 px

January 2022


Ingredients:

45 ml (2 parts) white rum
1/2 fresh lime cut into 4 segments
10 fresh mint leaves
2 teaspoons white cane sugar
Soda water
Garnish: with sprig of mint leaves and 1 lime slice.


Preparation:

Muddle the mint leaves, sugar and lime segments together in a collins glass. Add a splash of soda water and fill the glass with cracked ice. Pour in the rum and then top up the glass with soda water. Gently stir and garnish with a sprig of mint leaves and the slice of lime.
